title: Robbie.Maddison-Teamwork.FUEL.720P.h264.English
description: At first glance, Freestyle Motocross is an individual sport. But talent alone is not enough to get to the top: Robbie Maddison needs a reliable team to achieve its ambitious goals. His girlfriend/fiance, his coach, his mechanic, his manager and his friends - they are all part of a strong team that wants to end up near the front in the Red Bull X-Fighters back in the standings ...
